node.text: A special package available on any Super Air Nautique model, the Coastal Edition includes corrosion-resistant features throughout the boat that protect vital parts from the abuse of saltwater use. Whether or not you utilize your Nautique in a tropical paradise, an intra-coastal or marsh waterway, the Coastal Edition keeps your Nautique as happy as you are riding in it.

node.text: Due to extenuating circumstances, we regret to announce the Nautique Southwest Regatta taking place on September 17th-19th has been cancelled for this year. node.text: Nautique Boats and @thewwa have been monitoring the current situation regarding the COVID-19 global pandemic. Out of an abundance of caution, we have made the decision to move the dates for the Nautique WWA Wakeboard World Championships presented by @yanmarmarine and the Nautique Masters Wakesurf Championships presented by @yanmarmarine from August 25-28 to September 16-19. For more information, please visit the link in our bio! 🏆

node.text:
Another successful Nautique Regatta! What an incredible time here in Texas for the @nautiquesouthcentralregatta! A huge thanks to everyone that came out and enjoyed this one-of-a-kind event! #NautiqueSCRegatta @thewwa 
Another special thanks to our incredible dealers who supported this event! @buxtonmarine @sailandskitx @docksidemarinetx @norrismarine
